STATE
v.
TAYLOR 2018-0797 Supreme Court of Ohio. May 21, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On motions for admission pro hac vice of Louis Fisher, Samuel Spital, and Walter Kerrel Murray. Motions granted. Pursuant to Gov.Bar R. XII(4), counsel shall file a notice of permission to appear pro hac vice with the Office of Attorney Services within 30 days.
